description:
Processed from dataset named hlsp_heritage_hst_acs-wfc_m51_f814w_f555w_f435w_v1_drz, found at:

https://hla.stsci.edu/hlaview.html#Inventory|filterText%3D%24filterTypes%3D|query_string=m51&posfilename=&poslocalname=&posfilecount=&listdelimiter=whitespace&listformat=degrees&RA=202.484170&Dec=47.230560&Radius=0.075000&inst=ACS&inst=WFC3&imagetype=color&prop_id=&spectral_elt=&proprietary=both&preview=1&output_size=256&cutout_size=12.8|ra=&dec=&sr=&level=&image=&inst=ACS%2CACSGrism%2CWFC3%2CWFPC2%2CNICMOS%2CNICGRISM%2CCOS%2CWFPC2-PC%2CSTIS%2CFOS%2CGHRS&ds=

Processed in PI with minimal cleanup in linear, a little bit of HDRMT post stretch and some color work to enhance structural contrast. No detail enhancements or sharpening of any kind - the data is so gorgeous that I didn't want to risk taking anything away from it. :-P Take a look at full rez, but be warned: the image file is pretty large, even after a 50% resample.
title: M51 from Hubble Legacy Archive data
